<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.8.8">
<l>mēviyep pālumviṇ ṇōrvaṇaṅka vētamu raipparmun nīrmaṭantai</l>
<l>tēviyap pālatir caṅkamippāl cakkaram maṟṟivar vaṇṇameṇṇil</l>
<l>kāviyop pārkkaṭa lēyumoppār kaṇṇumva ṭivune ṭiyarāyeṉ</l>
<l>āviyop pāriva rārkkoleṉṉa vaṭṭapu yakarat tēṉeṉṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Celestials, joining [together in] all direction, chant the Vedas as they bow.</l>
<l rend="indent">At that side</l>
<l>Is the lady goddess [who rose from] the ocean [and] the trumpeting conch;</l>
<l rend="indent">the discus is on this side.</l>
<l>Moreover, if we number his attributes, he is like the blue lily;</l>
<l rend="indent">he is very like the sea; [his] eyes and body are of a tall man.</l>
<l>When I asked “Who is this who is like my life breath?”</l>
<l rend="indent">he answered, “I am he in the house of the eight-armed [Lord].”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
